00:04:16.150 --> 00:04:21.280
BALIK-ADAM ADASI – MERMAID CAFE  
CORAL HILL  

00:04:17.370 --> 00:04:18.680
Madam Sharley,  

00:04:18.680 --> 00:04:21.280
Luffy-chin ve arkadaşları  
